title: Dataiku support ticket sep 19
content:
SELECT NEXT value FOR "PD_OPS"."OPTR"."REST_DAY_PART_PLAN_SK" AS rest_day_part_plan_sk,
        '${vperioddate}'::timestamp AS etl_crtd_updt_ts,
       fd.cal_dt AS cal_dt,
       tp.tm_day_part_plnr_sk AS tm_day_part_plnr_sk,
       dp.day_part_sk AS day_part_sk,
       bu.ent_bus_unit_sk AS ent_bus_unit_sk,
       ii.item_sk AS item_sk,
       bu.bus_unit_cd AS bus_unit_cd,
       bu.chld_ent_prty_id AS chld_ent_prty_id,
       ii.wb_item_cd AS wb_item_cd,
       ISNULL(p.totalpred,0) AS ttl_plan_qty,
       ISNULL(p.dineinpred,0) AS dine_in_plan_qty,
       ISNULL(p.drivethrupred,0) AS drv_thru_plan_qty,
       v.totalvar AS ttl_var_amt,
       v.dineinvar AS dine_in_var_amt,
       v.drivethruvar AS drv_thru_var_amt,
       0 AS ttl_sls_qty,
       0 AS dine_in_sls_qty,
       0 AS drv_thru_sls_qty
  FROM "QA_OPS"."ADMIN"."DAYPARTPLANNER_dpp_variances_dataiku" as v
  JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT chld_ent_prty_id, ingredid, grouptype FROM "QA_OPS"."ADMIN"."DAYPARTPLANNER_lu_recipeingred_dataiku") as ri
    ON v.chld_ent_prty_id = ri.chld_ent_prty_id
   AND v.ingredid = ri.ingredid
LEFT OUTER JOIN "QA_OPS"."ADMIN"."DAYPARTPLANNER_dpp_predictions_dataiku" as p
    ON v.PERIODDATE  = p.periodstart
   AND v.chld_ent_prty_id = p.chld_ent_prty_id
   AND v.ingredid = p.ingredid
  JOIN (SELECT ent_bus_unit_sk, chld_ent_prty_id, bus_unit_cd,
               CASE WHEN end_of_day_tm = '!' THEN '15:00'
                    ELSE end_of_day_tm END AS end_of_day_str
          FROM "PD_OPS"."OPTR"."SYN_DIM_BUSINESS_UNIT"
         WHERE bus_unit_type_cd IN ('CR','CC','FR')
           AND last_rec_ind = 1
           AND end_of_day_tm <> '24:00') bu
    ON v.chld_ent_prty_id = bu.chld_ent_prty_id
  JOIN "PD_OPS"."OPTR"."SYN_DIM_CALENDAR_DATE" as fd
    ON TO_CHAR(v.PERIODDATE + CAST((date_part('hour', bu.end_of_day_str::time)) || ' hours' AS interval), 'MM/DD/YYYY') = fd.cal_dt
  JOIN "PD_OPS"."OPTR"."SYN_TIME_DAY_PART_PLANNER" as tp
    ON TO_CHAR(v.PERIODDATE, 'HH24:MI:SS') = TO_CHAR(tp.strt_tm, 'HH24:MI:SS')
   AND ri.grouptype = tp.pd_type_id
  JOIN (SELECT item_sk, wb_item_cd
          FROM optr.syn_dim_item
         WHERE istrue(LENGTH(TRANSLATE(wb_item_cd, '0123456789', '')) = 0
           AND LENGTH(wb_item_cd) > 0)
           AND last_rec_ind = 1) ii
    ON v.ingredid = ii.wb_item_cd
